articles.title: UK air traffic meltdown 'one in 15 million' event - Reuters UK
articles.description: An air traffic meltdown that hit Britain last week was caused by a "one in 15 million" event, the boss of traffic control provider NATS said, after it cited a flight plan with two identically named markers as the reason for the chaos.
